page_title: Azure OpenAI default content safety policies
page_description: Learn about the default content safety policies that Azure OpenAI uses to flag content.
chunk_title: Vision models: GPT-4o, GPT-4 Turbo, DALL-E 3, DALL-E 2

Characters    | Prompts                | N/A                 || Profanity                                         | Prompts                | N/A                 |In addition to the above safety configurations, Azure OpenAI DALL-E also comes with prompt transformation by default. This transformation occurs on all prompts to enhance the safety of your original prompt, specifically in the risk categories of diversity, deceptive generation of political candidates, depictions of public figures, protected material, and others.
